      "I think we should change all ops, including multi-row ops, to have a `changes` field, which is an array of objects of the form `old_val => ..., new_val => ...`.  This would be a backwards-incompatible change, but it would make things more consistent (someone might not be 100% sure how many documents they're inserting when they write a query)."
